title: Paranormal Police - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 8/9/22

description:
George Noory and author Gare Allen stories of law enforcement officers who have had paranormal experiences they could not explain, including ghosts who call to report their own fatal accidents, demons in a hospital room, and a haunted tower where people committed suicide.
